      "content": "one day at a time... how am i supposed to do that when every single day is just going to be this same emptiness? it's not just a bad day, it's like the whole world has lost its color. i look ahead and i see nothing. just a long, exhausting stretch of nothingness. it feels impossible to keep going just to feel this much hurt over and over again.",
